1288
01:07:35,533 --> 01:07:38,033
-YEAH, WELL,
THAT'S TED AND DOUG.

1289
01:07:38,067 --> 01:07:41,033
-D-DO YOU THINK
IF THERE'S AN INVESTIGATION

1290
01:07:41,067 --> 01:07:44,333
