OUR DAUGHTER THINKS

1293
01:08:08,733 --> 01:08:12,167
THAT I'M A-A FUCK-UP,
AND YOU KNOW WHAT HURTS ME MOST

1294
01:08:12,200 --> 01:08:15,067
