1296
01:08:16,667 --> 01:08:19,533
-YOU'RE NOT A FUCK-UP.

1297
01:08:22,167 --> 01:08:27,233
-I WAS GONNA GO IN EARLY TODAY
AND, UH, SNOOP AROUND THE CAVE

1298
01:08:27,267 --> 01:08:30,533
