01:10:43,367 --> 01:10:46,800
-NO, I-I DID MY HOMEWORK.

1337
01:10:46,833 --> 01:10:50,400
AND, UH, SEEMS THAT, UH,

1338
01:10:50,433 --> 01:10:54,100
