GET OFF OF ME!

1377
01:13:32,167 --> 01:13:33,600
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

1378
01:13:33,633 --> 01:13:36,300
GET OFF!

1379
01:13:37,533 --> 01:13:39,600
GET OFF OF ME!

1380
01:13:39,633 --> 01:13:40,767
JESUS!

1381
01:13:40,800 --> 01:13:42,133
-NO!

1382
01:13:42,167 --> 01:13:44,400
-FUCK!

1383
01:13:44,433 --> 01:13:47,667
